reviewText: All the places we saw when we were there! Fantastic product.

I was curious to what Kauai looked like.  This beautiful HD video gave me a great overall view of the island.  I especially liked the video map that showed me where the locations were that were shown on the video. I also liked the WATERFALL HUNTER episode showing me how to get to a couple of waterfalls in Kauai.  I love waterfalls and will check out the other episodes on this companies other videos of the other islands.  Enjoy.
